			bindings = <
// +----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+                                                 +----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+----------+
// |          |          |          |          |          |          |                                                 |          |          |          |          |          |          |
   &trans     &none      &none      &kp PG_UP   &kp HOME  &none                                                        &none      &none      &kp UP     &none      &none      &none
